            <span id="First_Paragraph_Mod">
            After I graduated from high school, I got a job in Fort Smith with a plumbing company that my dad bought plumbing supplies from. My job there was to type up invoices for the people who bought the supplies. <br />
            </span>
            <div id="boxmodex3" class="clearfix">
